#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:6 a5ad2682cc094c1ab5539f1d40553d95
msgid ""
"MonoChain is the helper class for Chain Mono display devices on the Chain"
" bus. It provides methods to control an 8 x 8 monochrome display, "
"including pixel drawing, full-screen buffer refresh, ASCII character "
"display, scrolling text, brightness, and rotation."
msgstr ""
"MonoChain 是 Chain 总线上 Chain Mono 显示设备的辅助类。它提供控制 8 x 8 "
"单色显示屏的方法，包括像素绘制、全屏缓冲区刷新、ASCII 字符显示、滚动文本、亮度和旋转。"

#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:11 b67e21f7ddfc49daba3d5d3d60abdb2a
msgid "Support the following products:"
msgstr "支持以下产品："

